          },
          "reviewBody": "I am an alumnus of TAS.I can just say that this is one of the best school for the children. Awesome teachers, safe campus with a blend of academic and co-curricular activities for the overall development of a child.I always miss my English,Maths and Geography teachers who always believed in creating global citizens.Music periods,Sports periods were just nostalgic. We never miss any chance of running back to school to relive the moments of TASian.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
