            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am a former student of TAS. As such, I have had many wonderful experiences in this school. The teaching faculty is amazing, as the teachers are dedicated to helping the child not only understand the theoretical aspect of a concept, but also to grasp the real-life applications of it. They are very thorough with their teaching and I can say from personal experience that the teachers guide their students every step of the way. With a variety of activities like music, games and a multitude of competitions, they always ensure the child is active and has many learning experiences. The TAS family is full of love and care. I definitely enjoyed my time there with all my friends and teachers.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
